      Dual Licensing Model
    </title>
    <para>
      SilkPage is intended to support a classic dual-licensing structure:
      <emphasis>GPL for open-source use</emphasis> and
      <emphasis>commercial licensing for proprietary distribution,
      embedding, and support arrangements</emphasis>. This model only works
      when the commercial licensor has the necessary copyright control over the
      codebase and all redistributed third-party components have been reviewed.
    </para>
    <para>
      The repository-level policy and commercialization checklist are described
      in <ulink url="https://github.com/sindoc/silkpage/blob/main/COMMERCIAL-LICENSING.md">COMMERCIAL-LICENSING.md</ulink>
      and
